root = create_root_analysis(uuid=str(uuid.uuid4()), analysis_mode='test_groups'
    )
root.initialize_storage()
observable = root.add_observable(F_TEST, 'test_1')
root.save()
root.schedule()
engine = TestEngine()
engine.enable_alerting()
engine.enable_module('analysis_module_basic_test')
engine.controlled_stop()
engine.start()
engine.wait()
root = RootAnalysis(storage_dir=root.storage_dir)
root.load()
self.assertEquals(root.analysis_mode, 'test_groups')
self.assertEquals(log_count(
    'analysis mode for RootAnalysis({}) changed from test_empty to correlation'
    .format(root.uuid)), 0)
self.assertEquals(log_count('completed analysis RootAnalysis({})'.format(
    root.uuid)), 1)
use_db
